reviews.text: Food is relatively cheap for Indonesian in Hong Kong, but still food of seafood inside taste is adjust to Hong Kong poeole, and tasty

Good Indonesian food.
Take away option also available.
Service very good and quick.
Price of average dish varies from hkd 40 to Hkd70 so very good value for money 
Location nearby the Dragon Center in sham shui po
good authentic food
average prices, average food
Really good and authentic Indonesian food. Love the Rujak fruit salad and Bakmi Singkawang noodles. One of my go to places when craving for food from my home country.
